TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6f0eedcd-f435-45a8-8875-19f8b0b49ae4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b28145b2-8586-4234-abb0-2125dfe49195\">기분이 좋아지게 하는 물질</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c819ce96-a56e-4187-aa79-5f088bc5ca6f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-79bf2db5-6e43-4f97-970a-d4b3da196910\">통증을 해소해주는 물질</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9bd64267-eaf1-4702-b981-1b085b999f93\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-176554ec-1941-47bf-8cd1-8a2718952b8e\">신경흐름을 원활하게 해주는 물질 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-946e8304-d22b-4c8a-802d-e316caced173\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-654509e1-b010-4a62-940c-e7ecf4dd6806\">등등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-477052d2-9d99-4acf-849e-a3d949bc6fae\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b2f47835-438a-4b87-a229-fb6e2a39e8e9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bce78aa2-88be-4bf4-8370-b7f6858aa7d7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d590cf09-a9fc-4543-8aa2-05bdeec987c1\">그렇게 뇌에서 분비되는 물질은 전신에 작용을 하게 되죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a57286e4-da0c-47bf-b5f1-f341bd007146\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-744a23c7-c396-4483-b9b0-b16ee4619ed6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4b9f18c3-ab02-4ede-835c-bd8ca6646bf3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-600b10cf-8f43-4999-9b03-b731c3a5c8fb\">그래서 손발에 침을 맞았는데 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dc54de92-91c0-4921-a39e-ef28cab02f5d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6b3b12bf-ad18-4536-b6c6-da5e65c48255\">소화불량이 치료되고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ad8beb3d-0ebd-4f38-ba4b-e65ea4c77174\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8cca2b81-483c-4323-a379-31aeab97453b\">변비가 좋아지고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f5264171-9785-47df-8bee-2ef233e0029e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-184ce586-ce48-46f1-b5a1-a090e95e8e11\">불면증이 호전되며</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-84955329-5b64-4bf5-b77f-6657b4775762\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5b3ea8e1-5e70-4ac5-ab8f-ed18c74c6610\">인후통이 좋아지게 되요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6072b4c5-133b-44fd-aee1-8b608b2798a3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4840957a-0277-42a6-92e6-ed6a4796632e\">침을 맞으면 몸이 가벼워진다는 분도 있어요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f757a3e7-4575-4bce-8597-c8bb9a899002\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c63b8bdc-282e-4134-a187-7e7b5ca89f98\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e343d82c-beee-4d1d-b78a-6399104941c7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a62d3bbe-b60b-4cbf-9e93-c1f7d222fd6f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c43ba46f-0bd9-4acb-a7c4-ca79f09ae2e0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ea0d91a9-019e-4a36-954e-6ec933f779f6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-746a911c-a5e8-4eeb-95dd-1636c7aaa642\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4db0c2c8-165d-4a45-bf9f-9712b1c386b6\">침을 맞은 부위 뿐만 아니라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ca1b77cd-0058-417c-be30-8e9716e8273e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3b5f4332-3cbc-4651-bf20-4967adda3348\">뇌와 신경에도 영향을 주기에 전신의 다양한 질병을 치료할 수 있는겁니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a3747cb7-7a1b-45c3-80a5-bb0047f4c483\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-97ee7d29-3b02-493e-9f9a-cc2e4fbea4be\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cb795fa2-89fb-4a23-a624-a3a0cc269d75\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9116e8c6-5f75-4e46-b923-cf2240632187\">더 나아가 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-00efb960-722e-4611-a937-ce822c6c304a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a96eea80-7ba2-460e-94fa-f77cf86a101c\">침치료를 잘 활용하면 예상되는 질병을 예방하는데도 응용할 수 있겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ea18eab1-9191-44c2-b0d1-93995b58dcb5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7f5027ea-71b3-4cff-9ddc-74d23f883f59\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eeeff045-feb8-4b57-8b86-72a2c091f8e0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff- 